{"code":"1","message":"数据获取成功","value":{"previousExamTime":45,"previousExamName":"201906机器人四级实际操作真题","subjectLevelList":[{"id":4590,"createUser":null,"createTime":"2021-07-27 14:20:29","isDeleted":0,"updateUser":null,"updateTime":null,"version":0,"type":4,"title":"<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span>主题：</span></b><span>跟随机器人。</span><b><span><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span>器件</span></b><span>：三四级等级考试套件。</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span>要求</span></b><span>：</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span>1、</span><!--[endif]--><span>现场搭建小车车体。</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span>2、</span><!--[endif]--><span>通过超声波模块检测小车前方物体。</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span>3、</span><font face=\"Helvetica\">要求前方物体前后移动时小车随之前后移动，车载</font><font face=\"Helvetica\">LED常亮。</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span>4、</span><font face=\"Helvetica\">当前方物体超出小车</font><font face=\"Helvetica\">30厘米时小车停止，车载LED闪烁。</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span>5、</span><font face=\"Helvetica\">当前方物体距离小车只有</font><font face=\"Helvetica\">5厘米时小车停止，车载LED闪烁。</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span>6、</span><font face=\"Helvetica\">程序编写采用</font><font face=\"Helvetica\">C/C++语言，不得使用图形化软件编写。</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span>7、</span><!--[endif]--><span>小车的运动控制程序，不得采用库函数调用。</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span>8、</span><!--[endif]--><span>考试结束，考生将代码拷贝上交。</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span>说明：</span></b><b><span><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><spa